The paper presents a model that predicts where people look in images using deep neural networks and transfer learning. This topic is closely related to computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI), as well as machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper discusses the factors that contribute to the success of the model, which is relevant to human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
